SEARCH
Package hust.cs.javacourse.search.index

Class AbstractPostingList

java.lang.Object
hust.cs.javacourse.search.index.AbstractPostingList
All Implemented Interfaces:
FileSerializable, Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
PostingList
public abstract class AbstractPostingList extends Object implements FileSerializable
 AbstractPostingList是所有PostingList对象的抽象父类.
      PostingList对象包含了一个单词的Posting列表.
      必须实现下面接口:
          FileSerializable：可序列化到文件或从文件反序列化.
